cs.CY, cs.SE, cs.DC, cs.CR, cs.NI 

The paper discusses the challenges of adopting cloud computing in the enterprise, which falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR), network infrastructure (cs.NI), and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also introduces a toolkit to support decision-makers in identifying concerns and matching them with appropriate tools/techniques, which can be categorized under cybernetics (cs.CY) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
